com.ibm.zrl.idmx.showproof
Class Verifier

java.lang.Object
  com.ibm.zrl.idmx.showproof.Verifier

public class Verifier
extends java.lang.Object

The Idemix show-proof verification side. This class runs the various sub-proofs after getting the proof data from the prover.

proofSpec - Proof specification we're trying to verify.

theMessages - messages/strings that will be hashed during the proof, producing a Schnorr signature
theCommitments - list of Commitments held by the verifier
theReps - Representation objects the prover is proving knowledge of
theVerEncs - Encryption objects the prover is proving knowledge of
